    <h1>Privacy Policy for Walmart Offer Activator</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> February 10, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Walmart Offer Activator ("the Extension") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains our practices regarding data collection and usage.</p>

    <h2>2. No Data Collection</h2>
    <p><strong>We do not collect, store, or transmit any user data.</strong> The extension is designed to operate entirely within your browser without sending any information to external servers or third parties.</p>

    <h2>3. Extension Permissions and Usage</h2>
    <p>The Extension requires specific permissions to function correctly, which are used solely for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Host Permission (Walmart.com):</strong> Used exclusively to identify and activate available offers on the Walmart website.</li>
        <li><strong>Scripting/ActiveTab:</strong> Used only to interact with the elements on the Walmart page to automate the offer activation process.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <p>Since no data is collected or transmitted, there is no risk of your personal information being compromised through the use of this extension.</p>

    <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>

    <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <strong>ostaplernatovych@gmail.com</strong></p>

